            <li>Practice with a timer. If you go over 60 seconds, cut the middle paragraph to one sentence.</li>
            <li>Make eye contact (or look at the camera on Zoom) during the final sentence. That is your close.</li>
            <li>Pause for 2 seconds after "I am looking for..." to signal you are transitioning to the forward-looking part.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <h3 class="font-semibold text-primary text-lg mb-3">Custom Interview Questions</h3>
