            { q: "How do you manage a complex travel itinerary?", topic: "Travel logistics", answer: "I build a single-page itinerary with travel times between meetings, backup options, and local contact numbers. For international trips, I include visa requirements, currency notes, and timezone overlays." },
            { q: "How would you handle a situation where your executive double-booked themselves?", topic: "Problem-solving", answer: "I would assess which meeting is higher-priority, propose a reschedule for the other, and draft the rescheduling message. I would also add a buffer process to prevent it from happening again." },
