            { q: "Why are you leaving your current role?", topic: "Motivation", answer: "I left my role at a publicly traded cannabis company in January to refocus my career on industries where I can leverage my investor relations and biopharma experience long-term. It was a strategic decision, and I have been using the time to complete Salesforce training." },
